  "_comment_1": "Curated peer sets for the Comps Analyst. Order = priority (most relevant first). Targets are picked for BUSINESS-MODEL similarity, not just market-cap proximity — e.g. ADBE peers are creative/design + enterprise SaaS, not the cybersecurity giants that happen to share the GICS sub-industry. When no entry exists here, `services.valuation_service._derive_peers_by_classification` falls back to top-N-by-market-cap within the same sub_industry.",
